          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer139109334" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16871284525203937158">I allowed myself a long and slow read for this small memoir of one year during a woman&apos;s lengthy, 20 year convalescence from an unknown virus. That year was made special by the presence of a snail brought in from the woods outside by a visitor. The author, Elisabeth Tova Bailey, was unable to live in her own home at that time, was feeling alienated from life, her surroundings, and felt isolated. This small creature led her to a year of observation, learning, fostering, and companionship. I learn</span>
  <span id="freeText16871284525203937158" style="display:none">I allowed myself a long and slow read for this small memoir of one year during a woman's lengthy, 20 year convalescence from an unknown virus. That year was made special by the presence of a snail brought in from the woods outside by a visitor. The author, Elisabeth Tova Bailey, was unable to live in her own home at that time, was feeling alienated from life, her surroundings, and felt isolated. This small creature led her to a year of observation, learning, fostering, and companionship. I learned facts I never knew that I wanted to know about the life cycle of the snail. And also I've confirmed a fact I've learned for myself... that the human spirit will find the means if at all possible to sustain itself and that companionship can come in many forms.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16871284525203937158" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
