<li class='cover' id='bookCover_44279929'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/44279929-to-speak-for-the-trees"><img alt="To Speak for the Trees: My Life&#39;s Journey from Ancient Celtic Wisdom to a Healing Vision of the Forest" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1563335272l/44279929._SX98_.jpg" />
