<span id="freeTextContainer16845075068591042359">Elisabeth Tova Bailey’s essays and short stories have been published in <i>The Missouri Review</i>, <i>Northwest Review</i>, and the <i>Sycamore Review</i>. She has received several Pushcart Prize nominations and a Notable Essay Listing in <i>Best American Essays</i>. She lives in Maine.</span>

